Class OntologyTerms

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.ontology.algo.OntologyTerms
@Deprecated(forRemoval=true, since="2.0.2") public final class OntologyTerms extends Object
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
use OntologyGraph methods instead.
Helper class with static methods for navigating Ontology terms.
Implementation Note

The methods simply reduce the ontology visiting to visiting vertices int he underlying graphs via BFS.

Author:
Manuel Holtgrewe, Sebastian Koehler
